content:
abrown opened PR #2335 from fix-ci to main:

The changes in https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/2278 added SourceLocs to several x64 Inst variants; between when that PR was last run in CI and when it was merged, new instructions were added that require this new parameter. This change adds the parameter in order to fix CI.
